WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:03.882
- Previously on Gotham...
- You have five minutes, quiz kids.

00:03.969 --> 00:05.869
Wayne Enterprises runs Indian Hill,

00:06.031 --> 00:09.546
but who runs Wayne Enterprises?

00:09.664 --> 00:11.975
A weapon is en route
to destroy the city.

00:12.010 --> 00:14.976
I can't take on Nygma and Barbara

00:15.046 --> 00:16.513
and the rest of them by myself.

00:16.548 --> 00:17.847
Said you wanted to build an army, right?

00:17.883 --> 00:20.550
What about an army of freaks?

00:20.585 --> 00:21.885
Who ordered the hit on my father?

00:21.920 --> 00:23.186
Frank Gordon.

00:23.221 --> 00:25.655
- Your uncle.
- You have the right to remain silent.

00:28.527 --> 00:29.859
Dock 9C.

00:29.895 --> 00:31.327
It's where the weapon will be arriving.

00:31.363 --> 00:33.630
Jim, do I hear a favor coming on?

00:33.665 --> 00:36.299
What is coming into

00:36.334 --> 00:38.134
Dock 9C?

00:38.170 --> 00:39.969
Now I know who I am...

00:40.005 --> 00:41.271
I'm the Riddler.

00:42.374 --> 00:43.373
It's good to see you, too.

00:43.408 --> 00:45.141
How'd things go with Selina?

00:45.177 --> 00:47.544
This... is what I was made for.

00:47.579 --> 00:48.878
The clone is in place.

00:48.914 --> 00:50.413
Good evening, Alfred.

00:50.744 --> 00:52.148
And to you, Master Bruce.

00:52.184 --> 00:53.817
You need to join the Court of Owls, Jim.

00:53.852 --> 00:55.652
A woman named Kathryn is going to call.

00:55.687 --> 00:57.087
He would have been so proud of you.

00:57.122 --> 00:58.951
No!

01:00.559 --> 01:01.825
Kathryn, I presume.

01:01.860 --> 01:03.259
I killed my uncle.

01:03.295 --> 01:04.561
I make no apologies for it.

01:04.596 --> 01:05.922
Maybe it's time we meet.

01:05.947 --> 01:08.032
My thought exactly.

