01:35.966 --> 01:37.527
Hello?!

01:38.138 --> 01:39.395
Anyone home?

01:39.716 --> 01:42.458
When this guy gets home, we got
to ask him to kick on the heat.

01:42.563 --> 01:44.989
It's colder in here
than it is out there.

01:48.626 --> 01:50.140
Fascinating.

01:50.517 --> 01:52.398
I know you're hell-bent
on getting revenge

01:52.423 --> 01:53.562
on Nygma and all,

01:53.689 --> 01:56.626
and forming an army of freaks
is a great plan, I mean,

01:56.712 --> 01:57.981
it was my idea, but...

01:58.016 --> 02:00.136
Shh! Quiet.

02:00.401 --> 02:02.042
I think I hear something.

02:02.232 --> 02:04.128
Do you think it's him?

02:13.604 --> 02:15.905
Mr. Fries.

02:18.021 --> 02:19.112
Welcome home.

02:23.038 --> 02:24.817
I see you still hold me responsible

02:24.842 --> 02:28.118
for all of that awful monster rhetoric
I spewed during my campaign.

02:28.143 --> 02:30.299
You ran people like me out of Gotham.

02:30.682 --> 02:32.348
We both know I only said those things

02:32.384 --> 02:35.250
because that's
what the voters wanted to hear.

02:36.521 --> 02:38.477
Your experiments, Mr. Fries.

02:38.829 --> 02:41.719
You're trying to reverse
your condition, aren't you?

02:41.893 --> 02:43.500
I can help you.

02:44.089 --> 02:45.321
And why would you do that?

02:45.397 --> 02:47.616
My enemies took everything from me.

02:47.799 --> 02:49.499
Tried to murder me.

02:50.249 --> 02:52.186
You help me get my revenge,

02:52.452 --> 02:54.311
and when I take back
my throne, I will give you

02:54.382 --> 02:57.537
every resource you need to free
yourself from this icy prison.

03:01.178 --> 03:02.842
Even if I wanted to say yes,

03:02.867 --> 03:05.293
I can only survive
a few hours outside the cold

03:05.318 --> 03:06.783
without my suit.

03:07.512 --> 03:10.471
And you don't have it
because it's been locked away

03:10.496 --> 03:14.412
in a Wayne Enterprises black site
ever since you escaped Indian Hill.

03:15.893 --> 03:17.370
Ivy?

03:17.529 --> 03:18.901
Oh.

03:21.346 --> 03:22.523
Ta-da.

03:22.651 --> 03:23.666
My suit.

03:30.000 --> 03:34.413
So, Mr. Fries, will you join us?

